high_descs: Turn right, then left, then right again to face the stove.
Grab the mug that is on the left on the counter.
Turn around the walk forward and face the fridge on the right.
Chill the mug in the fridge for about 5 seconds.
Turn right and head back to the stove but face left this time.
Place the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place the chilled mug in the coffee machine.

high_descs: turn around, walk to the corner,turn left, walk to the stove
grab the cup by the stove
turn around, walk to the refrigerator,
open the refrigerator, put the cup in, wait a while, take the cup out
turn right, walk to the coffee machine on the left
put the cup in the coffee machine
anns.task_desc: cool the cup in the refrigerator, put the cup in the coffee machine

high_descs: Face the opposite direction and cross the room to the far wall, then go left to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up the mug from the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn around to your left and go forward until you come to the fridge on your right, then turn right to face the fridge.
Put the mug center front on the top shelf of the fridge, then take it back out.
Turn right and go forward to the stove, then turn left to face the coffee maker.
Put the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug onto a coffee maker.
